    <h1 class="ph-title">Beyond crude oil</h1>
    <div class="ph-sub">The Gulf corridor moves more than crude. LNG, helium, naphtha, ammonia, diesel, jet fuel — all flow through the same chokepoints. When Hormuz closes, they all stop together. The downstream consequences reach semiconductor fabs, fertiliser plants, airlines and power grids.</div>
    <div class="ph-src">Sources: IEA Oil Market Report March 2026 · QatarEnergy · GIIGNL · USGS Mineral Commodities · IFA · IATA · S&P Global Platts · Argus Media · March 2026</div>
  </div>
</div>

